article_id:1586,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing the Next Summon Showcase: Dragon Special!,image_path:,message:<div>The next Summon Showcase: Dragon Special kicks off <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1600668000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>The appearance rates for featured 4★ and 5★ dragons will be boosted.</div><div><br></div><div>This showcase will be available from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1600668000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186399"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured Dragons:</div><div>
