						<li>One of the six legendary Greatwyrms who once<br>accompanied the Founder King. Also known as<br>the Netherwyrm, he wandered the abyss of death<br>after his defeat, but now spreads his wings to<br>stop the Other and fulfill his liege's dearest wish.</li>
